Hello All,

I have created end-to-end ML projects and posted them on Github, however, it didn't help in getting a role in ML. So I thought, doing a certification would make my profile stronger. Banking on it thought of preparing for a 'Google ML Professional' certificate.

Am I on the right path? I am not sure, as I am doing everything on my own. Please share your advice.

Background :

I am an experienced senior software developer based out of CANADA wanting to do a career switch to Applied ML.

Appreciate your help and support.

Thanks!!
